title: Micro Mart - 12 March 2015
description:
The UKs only Weekly IT magazine. 100 Pages of news, reviews, features and bargains. Micro Mart's aim is to inform, entertain and involve enthusiasts of all ages and to share our passion for computing with them in a humanised, opinionated and accessible manner. 

Since its launch in 1985, Micro Mart has been the first place users look for the UK's best and most up-to-date computer deals.

Genre: Magazine
